          <h4>Retest and recalibrate</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Retest your 2–3 priority markers — and optionally the full panel — at 90 days</li>
            <li>Compare against your baseline to measure intervention response</li>
            <li>Upload new results to the analyzer and compare your longevity score — the trend across tests is more informative than any single result</li>
            <li>Adjust your protocol based on response and identify the next set of targets</li>
          </ul>
